text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?
text.Response A: To see your page likes on Facebook, go to your Facebook page and click on the 'Likes' button in the left-hand menu. From there, you can see the total number of likes your page has, as well as a breakdown of where those likes are coming from. You can also access a more detailed view by clicking on 'See All' under the 'Likes' button.
text.Response B:
Open Facebook on your computer or mobile device.
Click or tap on the Search field.
Type in the name of the page you're looking for.
Click or tap on the page from the search results.
Find the number of likes on the page.

Prompt

Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?

Response A

To see your page likes on Facebook, go to your Facebook page and click on the 'Likes' button in the left-hand menu. From there, you can see the total number of likes your page has, as well as a breakdown of where those likes are coming from. You can also access a more detailed view by clicking on 'See All' under the 'Likes' button.

Response B

Open Facebook on your computer or mobile device.
Click or tap on the Search field.
Type in the name of the page you're looking for.
Click or tap on the page from the search results.
Find the number of likes on the page.
